dmca.title: [1B5-0B0B8E3B-8B32] DMCA Complaint from Terry Silverman - InfinitiPhoto/JVC Pro
dmca.body:
_____  

From: Misha Fletcher [mailto:misha@netenforcers.com] 
Sent: Wednesday, November 23, 2005 3:06 PM
To: legal-response@theplanet.com
Subject: RE: [1B5-0B0B8E3B-8B32] DMCA Complaint from Terry Silverman -
InfinitiPhoto/JVC Pro



To Whom It May Concern:

 

Thank you for your response to this matter. I have checked your client's
website for compliance and I am showing that the image is still being used.
You can see this by going to the below url: 

http://www.infinitiphoto.com/viewitem.php?IndexID=6850
<http://www.infinitiphoto.com/viewitem.php?IndexID=6850&RefTag=streetprices>
&RefTag=streetprices

Please advise how you will be handling this further as your client did not
comply. 

Misha Fletcher
Letter Management
Net Enforcers, Enforcement Team
 <mailto:misha@netenforcers.com> misha@netenforcers.com 
compliance.management@netenforcers.com

The Online Enforcement Experts...... 

Statement of Confidentiality

The contents of this e-mail message and any attachments are confidential and
are intended solely for the addressee.  The information may also be legally
privileged.  This transmission is sent in trust, for the sole purpose of
delivery to the intended recipient.  If you have received this transmission
in error, any use, reproduction or dissemination of this transmission is
strictly prohibited.  If you are not the intended recipient, please
immediately notify the sender by reply e-mail  and delete this message and
its attachments, if any. Thank you.

 

  _____  

 

 

From: legal-response@theplanet.com
Sent: Mon, 14 Nov 2005 18:04:43 -0500
To: Compliance.Management@netenforcers.com, legalresponse2@theplanet.com
Subject: DMCA Complaint from Terry Silverman

To Whom It May Concern: 

This letter confirms that access to the materials referenced in your
below-pasted complaint has been disabled. 

Legal Response Team 
The Planet 
---------
Please see the attached document.
